# Phase 10: Bash Scripting Basics

## 1. What is Bash?

Bash = Bourne Again Shell
Default shell in Ubuntu.

---

## 2. Create Script

touch script.sh
chmod +x script.sh

---

## 3. Basic Script Structure

#!/bin/bash

echo "Hello World"

---

## 4. Variables

name="Lucy"
echo $name

---

## 5. User Input

read -p "Enter your name: " user
echo "Hello $user"

---

## 6. If Statements

if [ $user = "Lucy" ]
then
  echo "Welcome back!"
fi

---

## 7. Loops

for i in {1..5}
do
  echo $i
done
